==Second Mission: Restart Mission== Contestants will choose 1 of the given songs of different concepts that they are confident in; new teams of 9 are formed. Voting of each contestant is conducted during the performances. The winning team with the most total amount of votes will win a benefit of immunity from elimination in the 1st elimination round, regardless of overall vote rankings of the show, plus the chance to perform in Rain's comeback stage.
